https://www.troyhunt.com/only-secure-password-is-one-you-cant/

## Har passordet ditt blitt stjålet?
Check if you have an account that has been compromised in a data breach (Troy Hunt) 
https://haveibeenpwned.com/


81% of hacking-related breaches leveraged either stolen and/or weak passwords. (Verizon)
http://www.verizonenterprise.com/verizon-insights-lab/dbir/2017/
